{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"96f5e13a56","title":"毛泽东撰中央关于召开中共八届三中全会的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"71b663f72f","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":31,"articleId":"96f5e13a56"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8c46e7da01","type":"title","text":"毛泽东撰中央关于召开中共八届三中全会的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"96f5e13a56"},{"id":"8fbafab831","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"96f5e13a56"},{"id":"a40f6004f3","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、邓：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"96f5e13a56"},{"id":"4563fd754d","type":"paragraph","text":"此件请提政治局通过，发出。省属市委提名是否恰当，请酌。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"96f5e13a56"},{"id":"d7c2b45ef4","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛七月卅一日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"96f5e13a56"},{"id":"302c33efdb","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"96f5e13a56"},{"id":"2eda2e374e","type":"paragraph","text":"各中央委员、候补中央委员；各省委、中央直属市委；各地委；哈尔滨、长春、沈阳、抚顺、鞍山、旅大、济南、青岛、南京、杭州、广州、长沙、重庆、成都、兰州、西安、太原各省属市委：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"96f5e13a56"},{"id":"a771aadacc","type":"paragraph","text":"决定于今年九月下半月召开中共中央委员会第八届第三次中央全体会议。请各省委、中央直属市委、自治区党委、地委、上开省属市委选派代表一人参加，最好是第一书记。省级第一书记为中央委员或候补中央委员者，不再选派代表。议程主要为：(一)整风问题；(二)农村问题。特此通知，请各有资格到会的同志们在会前对此两项问题加以研究为盼。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"96f5e13a56"},{"id":"9ab9cfbe96","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共中央一九五七年八月一日","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"96f5e13a56"}],"page":{"id":"5caa0cd8b8","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"96f5e13a56","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}